{"tid":2119264,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有人葡萄而家易入大學，真係笑而不語","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:03:20.000Z","uid":51200,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f8dfffb78a4956e413abe169ff2e20791869935f","tid":2119264,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"無錯，而家係好易讀到<br />\n但大家都心知個社會環境係點<br />\n早幾年出世一定有著數過而家先讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你儲錢做走都快幾年<br />\n<br />\n重點係<br />\nDSE雞唔好開心住<br />\n遲幾年個環境應該慘到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得趁住有書讀，<br />\n要去增進<strong>英文</strong> +其他技能<br />\n英文係好撚好撚重要<br />\n見過太多on 9 hea足四年，英文都係廢到仆街<br />\n你地第日要走，<br />\n其實已經遲呢一代幾年<br />\n錢又搵少幾年丶經驗又搵少幾年<br />\n所以有流利英文聽寫能力係最必要既<br />\n<br />\n讀廢科讀唔到專科？讀完都唔知讀乜？唔撚緊要<br />\n求其拎個second low+流利英文<br />\n夠你屌打九成人<br />\n<br />\n記住，讀唔成書都好<br />\n學撚好英文啊！"},{"pid":"fc50981746592b6f246c9ac7b64b39d77404b504","tid":2119264,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"有幾易入，睇睇？<br />\n第一年全四都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b90461e7c89d537809994c600a13d2a295b7b0","tid":2119264,"uid":355064,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"睇錯有人以為葡萄牙大學易入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cebea963ea928ea372685f0680f5ac9cc64d918","tid":2119264,"uid":51200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fc50981746592b6f246c9ac7b64b39d77404b504","tid":2119264,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"有幾易入，睇睇？<br />\n第一年全四都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/